sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente
    participant API as FastAPI API
    participant SEC as Seguridad
    participant RAG as Servicio RAG
    participant VDB as PostgreSQL + pgvector
    participant LLM as OpenAI API
    participant OBS as Logs/Métricas

    C->>API: POST /v1/query
    API->>SEC: Validar API key y rate limit
    SEC-->>API: OK / Error
    API->>RAG: Procesar consulta
    RAG->>VDB: Embedding + similarity search
    VDB-->>RAG: chunks + scores + metadata
    RAG->>LLM: prompt + contexto
    LLM-->>RAG: respuesta generada
    RAG->>OBS: registrar latencia, tokens, trace_id
    RAG-->>API: answer + sources
    API-->>C: 200 OK